    "question_id" : 7672597,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>On my device, <code>TimeZone.getDefault()</code> is always returning the UTC time zone.</p>\n<p>I need to do this to get the user-configured time zone:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-kotlin prettyprint-override\"><code>TimeZone.setDefault(null)\nval tz = TimeZone.getDefault()\n</code></pre>\n<p>It will return the user-selected time zone.</p>\n"
  }, {
